---
title: "Incorporating Geo-Diverse Knowledge into Prompting for Increased Geographical Robustness in Object Recognition"
collection: publications
permalink: /publication/2024-geoknowledge
date: 2024-06-17
venue: 'IEEE/CVF Conference on Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (CVPR)'
paperurl: 'https://krbuettner.github.io/GeoKnowledgePrompting/'
---
We analyze how context in class text representations of VL models affects geographical robustness in object recognition. We propose to ensure geographical robustness in soft prompting through a new geography knowledge regularization method. \
